== Feature

* checkout a wiki page as a local file
* edit the file
* update the file
* commit the file to the wiki
* supported wiki and blog systems:
  * qwikWeb
  * Trac's wiki
  * PukiWiki
  * tDiary

== Requirements

* ruby 1.8.3 : http://www.ruby-lang.org/
* htree 0.4 : http://raa.ruby-lang.org/project/htree/
* GnuPG : http://www.gnupg.org/

